<p>
Reporting to the Chief Marketing Officer, the successful candidate will provide business stakeholders across the organization with in-depth analysis of customer behavior, site performance across platforms (e.g. desktop, tablet, mobile), and channel performance (e-mail, affiliate, paid search, social media, etc.). They will take the lead on optimizing channel attribution for paid and non-paid media while collaborating with Finance to develop lifetime value analyses for different customer segments. Last but not least, they will provide ongoing analyses to assess the efficacy of our Geek Points loyalty program.</p>
<p>
The Manager is well versed in b2c e-Commerce and direct marketing KPIs, is a strategic thinker when it comes to utilizing analytical tools to draw actionable conclusions, and knows how to develop analytical frameworks and processes from scratch.</p>
<p>
<strong>RESPONSIBILITIES</strong></p>
<ul>
