Extract, analyze, manipulate, and synthesize data from a variety of sources to measure and report on online behavior</li>
<li>
Collaborate with leads in various marketing areas&mdash;acquisition, customer marketing, and user experience&mdash;to implement best practices about a/b and multivariate testing related to site design, functionality enhancements, and the impact of promotions across channels (e.g. email, site, external paid media, etc.)</li>
<li>
