Develop a framework and execute analysis of lifetime value and performance tracking by customer cohort, including but not limited to source of initial customer acquisition</li>
<li>
Develop and distribute daily/weekly/monthly and ad hoc reports and collaborate across departments to fulfill ongoing reporting needs</li>
<li>
Maintain pulse on latest trends in web measurement strategies and tactics</li>
