<li>
Strong communication skills</li>
<li>
Excellent work ethic</li>
<li>
Good systems knowledge</li>
<li>
Strong Excel&nbsp; Skills</li>
<li>
Team Player</li>
<li>
Proficient in data entry</li>
<li>
Experience in e-commerce company is preferred but not required</li>
</ul>
<p>
This position is based out of Fairfax, VA. This is a paid internship ($12-15/hour, depending on experience) lasting up to 6 months, and can be part-time or full-time.</p>
